    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>et Iunoni <lb n="3"/>Reginae <lb n="4"/>vicani Mo<lb break="no" n="5"/>gontiacen<lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>es vici no<lb break="no" n="7"/>vi <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Viergötterstein einer Jupitergigantensäule; auf den Nebenseiten und der Rückseite Darstellungen der Fortuna, des Sol und der Luna. Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
